Don't wanna be late!

7
00:00:26,063 --> 00:00:26,912
There.

8
00:00:27,009 --> 00:00:28,977
Spike, did you grab my quill and ink?

9
00:00:29,526 --> 00:00:30,089
Check!

10
00:00:30,408 --> 00:00:31,197
Scrolls?

11
00:00:31,595 --> 00:00:32,240
Check!

12
00:00:32,539 --> 00:00:35,453
I've also packed a telescope,
apples, bananas, fruit punch...

13
00:00:35,453 --> 00:00:39,465
