17
00:00:50,124 --> 00:00:52,545
I'm sorry. I didn't hear you.

18
00:00:52,850 --> 00:00:56,416
That is why you are my number one assistant.

19
00:00:56,608 --> 00:00:58,213
Missed that! Huh...?

20
00:00:58,515 --> 00:00:59,746
I said...!

21
00:01:02,088 --> 00:01:03,943
Come on, let's get going.

22
00:01:04,649 --> 00:01:06,162
Wait! I almost forgot.

23
00:01:06,362 --> 00:01:09,873
I wanna bring the "Astronomical Astronomer's
Almanac to All Things Astronomy".

24
00:01:10,183 --> 00:01:12,403
The Astronomo-lomo homono what?

25
00:01:12,677 --> 00:01:17,339
You know that really old big blue book
on stars, moons, planets, the Universe...?

26
00:01:17,645 --> 00:01:18,870
Right. Check!

27
00:01:37,473 --> 00:01:40,614
Hey! What's taking my number one assistant so long?

28
00:02:23,410 --> 00:02:25,795
I was sure I put the astronomer's guide back.

29
00:02:25,795 --> 00:02:28,986
