different planets and stars tonight.

30
00:02:29,541 --> 00:02:32,307
Well... Maybe someone borrowed it?

31
00:02:32,507 --> 00:02:34,723
Besides, you don't need that book.

32
00:02:35,004 --> 00:02:37,908
You can already name
all the planets and stars, cause...

33
00:02:37,908 --> 00:02:39,204
...you're super smart and...

34
00:02:39,204 --> 00:02:40,622
...astronomically awesome!

35
00:02:41,214 --> 00:02:43,563
Thanks, Spike. You're such a flatterer.

36
00:02:43,769 --> 00:02:45,173
Yeah, I'm a sweet talker.

37
00:02:45,507 --> 00:02:48,060
And a number one assistant, right?

38
00:02:48,210 --> 00:02:48,959
Check!

39
00:02:56,779 --> 00:03:00,029
Wow, Twilight! You're lucky
to have such a rad assistant.

40
00:03:00,029 --> 00:03:02,239
I wish I had someone to do whatever I told them.

41
00:03:02,734 --> 00:03:04,382
Ooh! Ooh! Me! Me! Me!

42
00:03:04,382 --> 00:03:06,506
I'll do whatever you want, Rainbow Dash!

43
00:03:07,034 --> 00:03:08,775
Oh yeah, pipsqueak?

44
00:03:08,775 --> 00:03:10,860
How about taking out the trash?

45
00:03:11,226 --> 00:03:12,050
Yes, ma’am!

46
00:03:13,636 --> 00:03:16,544
Do we have Spike to thank again
for this amazing spread?

47
00:03:16,544 --> 00:03:18,356
Isn't he simply amazing?

48
00:03:18,912 --> 00:03:20,676
Oh, come on.

49
00:03:23,437 --> 00:03:24,682
I said come on.

50
00:03:24,882 --> 00:03:26,603
Little Spikey-wikey!

51
00:03:26,767 --> 00:03:30,509
Who knew that big ferocious dragon
started off so cutesy wootsy?

52
00:03:31,099 --> 00:03:35,727
Spike, you are such a little star,
that I had to make a little bow tie for you.

53
00:03:37,808 --> 00:03:41,739
Gosh. You guys are embarrassing me. Stop it.

54
00:03:42,892 --> 00:03:44,071
Twilight, your turn.

55
00:03:44,316 --> 00:03:45,740
Spike, that's enough.

56
00:03:45,945 --> 00:03:47,427
All right. That's enough.

57
00:03:47,514 --> 00:03:49,649
Hey, everypony! The show is starting!

58
00:04:08,095 --> 00:04:09,794
Wow...

59
00:04:13,154 --> 00:04:13,884
Huh?

60
00:04:30,115 --> 00:04:32,918
Wow! These cookies are deeleesh!

61
00:04:33,157 --> 00:04:34,288
Spike made them.

62
00:04:34,288 --> 00:04:37,275
