63
00:04:39,274 --> 00:04:39,882
Spike?

64
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:45,033
Ooh, poor little thing.

65
00:04:45,306 --> 00:04:47,937
Aww... He's worked himself to the bone.

66
00:04:48,137 --> 00:04:49,601
